        properties:
            description: "The wedding of Ser Edmure Tully and Roslin Frey at the Twins, which served as the occasion for the Red Wedding massacre."
        notes: "The marriage itself was legitimate, but the wedding feast became the Red Wedding — a massacre of Robb Stark and his forces orchestrated by Lord Walder Frey and Roose Bolton."
